  <brief_title>Left Atrium Substrate Based Ablation Plus Circumferential Pulmonary Vein Isolation to Treat Chronic Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Left Atrium Substrate Based Ablation Plus Circumferential Pulmonary Vein Isolation in the Treatment of Persistent and Long-standing Atrial Fibrillation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
